#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:1
msgid "E4172"
msgstr "E4172"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `invalid_regex_pattern`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`invalid_regex_pattern`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:5
msgid "Invalid regex pattern."
msgstr "无效的正则表达式模式。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:7
msgid ""
"This error happens when a `re\"...\"` literal or a regex pattern used by "
"`lexmatch` does not follow MoonBit's regex syntax. Regex literals are "
"checked at compile time, so syntax errors, unsupported assertions, "
"invalid ranges, and duplicate capture names are reported before the "
"program runs."
msgstr ""
"当 `re\"...\"` 字面量或 `lexmatch` 使用的正则表达式模式不符合 MoonBit 的正则语"
"法时，会出现此错误。正则表达式字面量会在编译期检查，因此语法错误、不支持的断"
"言、无效范围和重复捕获名称都会在程序运行前报告。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:12
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:14
msgid ""
"fn invalid_regex() -> Regex {\n"
"  re\"[a-z\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:18
msgid "The character class starts with `[`, but never closes with `]`."
msgstr "字符类以 `[` 开始，但没有用 `]` 闭合。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:22
msgid "Fix the regex syntax, or rewrite the pattern using a supported regex form."
msgstr "修正正则表达式语法，或使用受支持的正则表达式形式重写该模式。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4172.md:24
msgid ""
"fn valid_regex() -> Regex {\n"
"  re\"[a-z]\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
